							<div id="post-62556" class="post post-62556 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-china category-economics category-government category-health-care category-international category-public-health tag-china tag-clark-merrefield tag-coronavirus tag-coronavirus-epidemic tag-coronavirus-pandemic tag-dow-jones tag-economy tag-epidemic tag-global-economy tag-hubei tag-merrefield tag-outbreak tag-pandemic tag-stock-market tag-stock-market-crash tag-u-s-economy tag-wuhan">
